**Recommendation:** Implement URL scheme validation to only allow safe protocols:

function isUrlSafe(url) {
  try {
    const parsed = new URL(url);
    const allowedSchemes = ['http:', 'https:', 'mailto:'];
    return allowedSchemes.includes(parsed.protocol);
  } catch {
    return false;
  }
}

Update linkService.js lines 59 and 154 to use isUrlSafe() instead of just new URL(). This prevents javascript:, data:, file:, and other dangerous URI schemes.

